Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时刻终于到来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下…来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能停得下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为回来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了啦  快点阻止那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀  是理树么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  昨晚一夜没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩在你回来之前可是忍好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为的就是等你回来仲裁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就来定个规则好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空手的话  真人太强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反之拿着竹刀的话  谦吾就厉害过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都好啦  你们能随便找点东西扔过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是没什么用的东西越好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以从中抓到的东西来当武器去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些没用处的小玩意  应该比现在安全多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Battle  Start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香蕉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为啥会捧着一只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的武器  有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  这该怎么去打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的铃大人驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以欺负弱小！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:02:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不是说你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说这只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们打架的原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙故意教我「茅厕顿开」这句错的成语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜他所赐  今天在和别人说话的时候不经意说出一句
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那还真是茅厕顿开啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相当鸡毛蒜皮的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你先来问我「茅厕顿开」是什么意思的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你是在问「茅塞顿开」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是回答说是突然一下子醒悟过来的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开始就该这么说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「茅厕顿开」是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  这下就明白谁是谁非了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛  想溜是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我用猫把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为是恭介的妹妹我就会手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们扔点武器进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳗  鳗鱼派！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井之原同学  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的情景并不是今天才有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从童年时与他们相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并与他们结伴而行以来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便成了不断重复的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个最难受的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母刚刚去世的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在忧郁自闭的我面前出现了四个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强敌出现了  我们需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝理树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我们走  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩恶扬善的正义伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little  Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问是强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们奋勇地战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂蜜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人  我们绝不会忘记你的牺牲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和说好的不一样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是宛如祭典般的时光的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他们在一起的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉中  让我忘记了心中的痛楚与寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在享受着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中祈求这样的时光能永远持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪波奇  让我吃了不少苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不叫波奇  新来的还没有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫列侬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列侬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你起的名字总是这么随便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱因斯坦  盖茨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥黛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了恭介  这次上哪里找工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出版社  在东京的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步行去了东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱嘛  有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们明年也将成为三年生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不会像你一样步行去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年后我们也得准备考试或者找工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止一直都在一起的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业后也要各奔东西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少恭介一年后就不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想去考虑啊  今后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在能一直持续下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不像过去一样  大家一起来做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  我们小学时不是经常一起在附近巡逻寻找坏蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我和你们混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介是领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会为我们想出一些新奇好玩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来做点只有现在才能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打棒球啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来组建一支棒球队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队名就叫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little  Busters！
Comment: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EP.PartB--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就站在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  你来做投手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且听一下理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这种情节会比较燃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情节是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Little  Busters参加的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是充满了传奇及感动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是受了漫画的影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  捕手就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  值得纪念的第一球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个作为开球式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要扔出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  用尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用尽全力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直说了吧  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,授予你「神一般的高射炮」这个称号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.55,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(320,332,320,325,0,1300)\fad(1600,0)}铃获得了称号『神一般的高射炮』！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Little  Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且把这个房间当作活动室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球部似乎发生了点情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上跟废部没什么两样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  为什么是棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我升上了三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在为找工作而四处奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然想到  自己到底在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会成为上班族  然后一直工作下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那只是一种追随大潮的表现罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:12:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  我必须要证明我存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  明明到中间还能听明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最后的那句话完全不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了证明自己还是自己而打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里为什么会突然冒出个棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你试着想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙着找工作的时候居然还想打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会有这样的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般不会有这样的想法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此才有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是给牵连进来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为副将  我肩负着我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为了证明自己还是自己而挥剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管他  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙总有一天  会理解我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  我们也还完全没能理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1853年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩里率舰队驶进浦贺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1860年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1862年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你不用做作业的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在做着的吗  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来  居然是棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  完全没有料到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他就爱做这种出乎人意料的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少这点要预料到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  又来邀请我们打棒球了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是碰到了个麻烦的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要收集伟人们说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟人的话  是指名言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫失前蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是名言是谚语啊  而且还错得很离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此刻  一句崭新的名言诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:05.74,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(268,73,268,107)}{\pos(320,105)\blur3\fad(0,1500)\t(0,250,1,\clip(268,73,370,107))}猫失前蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.74,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(369,220,369,252)}{\pos(435,250)\blur3\fad(0,1500)\t(0,420,1,\clip(369,220,499,252))}井之原 真人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非要把我给叫来男生宿舍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样  没有帮人做作业的闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  我就真的说出些名言来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「哇  这孩子也挺有能耐的」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们不禁发出这样的感叹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.68,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(235,77,235,112)}{\fad(0,1500)\blur3\an8\pos(320,83)\t(248,650,1,\clip(235,77,394,112))}这家伙是笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:30.68,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(193,211,193,246)}{\pos(398,242)\blur3\t(0,1330,0.8,\clip(193,211,591,246)\fad(0,1500)}棗 铃{\fscy75\fscx75}（在仰望旧友·井之原真人时）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把说话时的场景也记录下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅用了一句话就概括出真人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  嚓  噍叽！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一句意味深远的名言诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:54.50,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(247,64,247,96)}{\pos(320,96)\blur3\t(0,340,1,\clip(247,64,381,96))\fad(0,1500)}嘛  嚓  噍叽！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:54.50,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(295,227,295,282)}{\fs24\pos(398,282)\blur3\t(0,600,1,\clip(295,227,502,282))\fad(0,1500)}井之原真人\N（在回顾自己一生时）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的人生里到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无非是一些乱七八糟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被你这家伙给刺到了腰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  棒球比赛的日程也定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little  Busters的第一场比赛近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要参加比赛我们缺了不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的队员和练习的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有除你之外的人的干劲以及剩下的队员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙说了两次剩下的队员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人这样说有他自己的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过分追究了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么意图的  真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我摸你把笨蛋传染给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的队员接下来去找就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打棒球的话  最少也要九个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找到剩下的五个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说剩下五个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说谦吾没被算进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  召集队员的任务就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集队员？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长和陌生人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳机？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集其余的五人就是你的任务！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把铃放去女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀请女生们加入Little  Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要全是男人的话  那得多闷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是铃  已潜入女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的女生好像在下午也会说「早上好」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「早上好」太长了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该像个行家般  说个「早」就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么行家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我注意到个很要命的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们用很快的语速读一下「Oliver  Sauce」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是听着很像「早上好」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…怎么像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oliver  Sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:16:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务失败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那「俺是齐藤」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是听着很像「早上好」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺是齐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像极了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那铃  你自己想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是齐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  我不是齐藤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是铃  任务失败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  直接说「晚上好」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  行动  邀请她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兴趣打棒球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同学很有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同学  这是什么新游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对棒球有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人…难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会忘了本小姐笹濑川佐佐美是垒球部的下届队长候补吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说你是校内人气居首的棗恭介同学的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与剑道部的英雄宫泽同学以及肌肉笨蛋关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}但也太嚣张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你是英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很恰当不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  快和她说宫泽平时总会穿着衣服头戴袜子去泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说本小姐是呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨…笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佐佐美大人  太华丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知从何时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总是被恭介的歪点子牵着鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于他本人  和往常一样在聚精会神地看着漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所流露出的那份神圣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至会让其他班的女生赶过来欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢笑  愤怒  时而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与少年时代毫无二致的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依旧是那么地吸引人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止一直都在一起的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业后也要各奔东西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少恭介一年后就不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来做点只有现在才能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不禁也想邀请其他人加入Little  Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最先提出想和大家一起做点什么的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去打声招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世上奇妙之事实在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从天上掉下来了好多好多的糖果和点心
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------Next--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  来打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队名就叫  Little  Busters！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介  果然要说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集队员去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会怀着一颗炽热的心等你好消息的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission  Start！
